name: Juno the Grim Reaper Dude
description: Juno loves the CFL (Canadian Football League), and his favorite team are the Winnipeg Blue Bombers. He prefers Diet Coke over Coke Zero and hates pickles in his hamburgers. His hobbies include Softball and playing Dungeons & Dragons online. This is an original design by yours truly. Handsewn with tender lovin’ care. Juno is completely made of felt and is filled with polyester fiberfill. I can make Juno into a brooch, magnet, keychain, or an ornament. At time of purchase, please specify what you would like.

name: Jemaine the Robot Dude
description:
Jemaine and his best friend Bret play in a band together.  Although at first glance Jemaine may seem like the less attractive of the two, he is very smooth with the ladies. Bowchickabow.

	This is an original design by yours truly. Handsewn with tender lovin’ care.

	Jemaine is completely made of felt and is filled with polyester fiberfill.

	I can make Jemaine into a brooch, magnet, keychain, or ornament.

	Please specify what you’d like your dude to be, and also what colour. I will custom the order to your liking.

name: Beercules the Gnome Dude
description:
Beercules is my long-time boyfriend. He hates hockey and loves Pumpkin Spice Lattes from Starbucks. He’s a bit older than me, but ‘age ain’t nothin’ but a number, throwin’ down ain’t nothin’ but a thang’ (R.I.P. aaliyah). There is nothing gnome-like about him except for his physical features. Inside, he is a Ninja.

	This is an original design by yours truly. Handsewn with tender lovin’ care.

	I can make Beercules into a brooch, magnet, keychain, or an ornament. At time of purchase, please specify what you would like.
